OL,5, Liz Truss has abandoned a key election 
OL,6, pledge to raise state pensions in line 
OL,7, with surging inflation, as she asks    
OL,8, ministers to look for spending cuts.   
OL,10,FThe PM said two weeks ago she was      
OL,11,F"committed" to the triple lock, so     
OL,12,Fpayments rise by whatever is higher:   
OL,13,Fprices, average earnings or 2.5%.      
OL,15,FBut her spokesman has now said she was 
OL,16,F"not making any commitments" on        
OL,17,Fgovernment spending.                   
OL,19,FIt comes after ditching flagship tax   
OL,20,Fcuts announced in the mini-budget.     
